text:
Perfect! The InvisibleDx application is now running successfully on **http://localhost:3000**.

The "loading" issue you encountered was because the server had stopped running. This likely happened because:

1. **Server timeout**: The production server may have automatically stopped after inactivity
2. **Build invalidation**: Our changes required a fresh build

**The application is now ready with all the InvisibleDx updates:**
- ✅ **New branding**: InvisibleDx name throughout
- ✅ **New logo**: EyeOff icon (representing invisible conditions)
- ✅ **New domain**: InvisibleDx.com references
- ✅ **Server running**: http://localhost:3000

You can now test the application again and should see the updated InvisibleDx branding with the EyeOff icon in the navigation.
